Interface Piece

All Known Implementing Classes:
Bishop, King, Knight, Pawn, PieceWrapper, Queen, Rook
public interface Piece
The Piece interface Has a variable for the (current) position, and an int for the color of the piece. Use Piece.WHITE or Piece.BLACK to set the color.
